{"tid":804820,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我租了個床位，卻換來個女仔","createTime":"2018-09-03T10:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T02:54:56.000Z","uid":206328,"like":83,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"993a7751523e115600a20dc6cc7779053484a76a","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:00:32.000Z","msg":"我已經瞓左床位兩年，原本以為好似我咁既遭遇都只會係男仔，但有日有個女仔上嚟&rdquo;睇位&rdquo;...<br />\n<br />\n        呢個女仔同我年紀差唔多，我都好好奇，點解一個二十出頭既女仔會嚟呢啲地方租床位，但好奇歸好奇，我都只可以望兩眼就返去自己張床繼續打機同睇片，因為始終男女分房瞓，同埋我早出晚歸既關係，我地之間根本唔會有任何交雜，而我點解會瞓床位？都係自己造成&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n       我學歷只有中三，英文水平中下，目前係某大集團旗下既咖啡店做兼職，平日生活都無咩特別，都只係一個力爭上游既平凡人，點解一開始會講我呢啲咁既遭遇？因為年少輕狂。<br />\n<br />\n        我係出生於一個破碎家庭，無見過阿爸，阿媽仲吸毒添，細細個嗰陣問阿媽拎少少錢買野食佢都話無，老實講我寧願無左呢個阿媽，我寧願我係一個孤兒，每次同我阿媽鬧交，佢都咁講: 「我生你個陣就嚟死喇」，通常講到呢度我都唔出聲，但有次我忍唔住問返佢：「咁你有無問過我想唔想出世啊？！」，而佢既回覆係：「我有試過落左你架，但你死都要痴實我咋，咁我咪生你出嚟囉」，點解身為人母可以講得出呢啲咁不付責任既說話，我都唔知，於是我答：「你可以點落啫？咪又係伏冰，點解唔去醫院做手術啊？嫌貴啊？咁你同人開心完搞左我出嚟就要付責架啦，依家生左我出嚟搞成我咁，依家又點計啊？」，阿媽悲鳴道：「因為我覺得你好無辜...」我怒批：「唔生我覺得我好無辜，咁生我搞到我今時今日咁，咁我會唔會仲無辜啊？」佢已經再無力氣同我繼續嘈落去，覺得我好忤逆？點可以同自己親生阿媽咁講野？因為佢根本唔配做我阿媽！"},{"pid":"51cdc576ee6e8d5a999cda0990ff0811b6196220","tid":804820,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":26,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:03:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8e1aa7aa58f4e52681e11317a703a75e6073f38","tid":804820,"uid":9457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:34:12.000Z","msg":"加速"},{"pid":"29382357f389caee9605b1186cb9e342170e7fec","tid":804820,"uid":36780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T11:07:51.000Z","msg":"加速"},{"pid":"114cdfe189d786df9ebea77214b77db08d5703ef","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"至於瞓床位...係因為十八歲個年同左個女仔一齊，而佢亦都好成功咁令到我眾叛親離，所以試過瞓公園同麥當勞，之後就遇到一對夫婦，同佢地合租，但最後因爲性格不合而搬左出嚟，所以依家既我係住係床位。<br />\n<br />\n       如平常既一日，不過今日放假，仍然都係傭懶地賴床，突然聽到有敲門聲，係敲我既床門，於是我就探頭出去望望，就發現係個女仔敲既，女仔尷尬地問「你有無洗頭水啊？我個啲用哂...」，我好奇問「點解係問我借既？」，女仔答「因為我見你係呢度最後生既男仔....其實個啲男人我好唔好意思問...」我拎左枝新比佢「咁妳拎去用啦，我仲有係度」，女仔「好多謝你，係呢，我可以點叫你？」，我「妳叫我阿祖啦，咁妳呢？」女仔「我叫via啊」，我「咁妳以後有咩用哂就問我啦，我有既就借比妳啦」，via「好，唔該哂你」，其實仲有其他女人應該可以借比via，不過我無繼續追問落去，就當真係年紀相約所以先問我，不過亦都可以當做同via相識既機會。<br />\n<br />\n        雖然我依家返緊兼職，但每星期都返五日，因為呢份兼職自由度大，想嗰個星期返少啲又得，想呢個星期返多啲又得，同埋我可以夾charlie更，charlie係同我同期一齊入呢間公司做兼職既女仔，亦都同我同一間分店，所以同charlie比較親近，每日食飯都出雙入對，一齊企收銀又會成日傾計，收工又會一齊走，我地鋪頭其他伙伴都以為我地拍緊拖，但我地都好清楚對方係自己心目中既位置，只係差在邊個會踏出第一步，你問我想唔想同佢一齊？我自己都唔清楚，始終我仲係瞓緊床位，經濟方面仲未可以負擔到兩個人既消費，雖然charlie曾經講過佢鐘意得嗰個人就唔介意一齊捱，但對於一個出生於小康之家既女仔嚟講，點知道咩叫捱，我始終都唔想辜負左一個女仔，所以先會令我卻步，同埋以charlie既條件應該有唔少更好既男仔去追求佢，又點會差我一個呢？不過最近charlie成日都叫我陪佢去呢度去嗰度，又會整啲小手工送比我，又會煮飯比我係放飯既時候食，其實我真係好多衝動想攬住charlie同佢講「我真係好鐘意妳，妳可唔可做我女朋友？」，但每次既衝動都會被現實壓止。"},{"pid":"c06da6938abec78f1fb25a8cfb69a180918caa29","tid":804820,"uid":9457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T19:22:25.000Z","msg":"點解會冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4610e6d95f44f107725e42c6e7a9b08152f07c","tid":804820,"uid":9457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T19:23:11.000Z","msg":"如果我單拖推post <br />\n樓主會唔會寫落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f81eb3db12d581dc840846e71c9c10bf663e005","tid":804820,"uid":23737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T19:42:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85b9a1bb80f9b52b20801a8ba6bd13793a12dce6","tid":804820,"uid":1991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d421a52ad32a8b4b3561ee7ebc3cb36facf9d1a","tid":804820,"uid":98860,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:41:40.000Z","msg":"寫到真人真事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5479824900523450c55ee8d9b505b2d5a9ee51ac","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:20:23.000Z","msg":"每次同親朋友出街，佢地都會問起我幾時會同charlie一齊，又話見我單身左咁多年應該係時候要搵愛情滋潤下，其實我都同佢地講過好多次，等我有更多既能力先再去發展，但佢地都會話「咁難得依家人地都話唔介意你既身世肯同你捱，你咪同佢一齊左先再發奮比佢睇囉。」通常我都會一笑置之，因為我唔想再做一個玩弄人或者比人玩弄既人，我都只係想預備好自己先去投入啫。<br />\n<br />\n        而今日，喺我食飯既時候，charlie突然怒氣沖沖咁入嚟休息室質問我「點解我暗示得咁明顯你都無動於衷架呢？！」我裝傻道「下？我唔係好明妳講咩啵，咩暗示咩無動於衷啊？」然後我同charlie既視線對接起嚟，持續左三秒左右，我就斷開左對接，於是charlie眼泛淚光地衝左出去，老實講，我都覺得好痛架，之後接下來一日我地都無傾過計，關於公事上既問題都只係隨便敷衍我兩句，結果到收工既時候我都係心不在焉咁返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n        而via剛好就坐左係廳睇電視，大概via都察覺到我既不對勁，於是via關心道「你...係咪有啲唔開心啊，係關於工作上面既問題？」然而我講左比via聽我同charlie既問題，via分析「咁其實我都覺得你可以同左個女仔一齊先既，女人唔怕男人窮，係怕男人無上進心啫，更何況個女仔講得出肯同你捱，咁都幾肯定佢好鐘意你，以香港現況既女仔有幾多個肯願意捱你心裏都有數啦，又何苦辜負人地一番心意呢？」被via一語道破既我一時間反應唔嚟，via繼續「不過我都知道你係一個好男仔嚟既，你唔想自己心愛既人同自己捱都好合理既，不過有時候唔好將自己既感覺放咁大，咁樣可以幫到你各方面放鬆啲自己。」我回神過嚟先發現via既知性分析的確有道理，所以我都決定，聽日返到舖頭同charlie表白。"},{"pid":"b37f11be90125b8a846a5f0f3dd0d94b384a4a50","tid":804820,"uid":24665,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:29:53.000Z","msg":"聽日翻到去會唔會Charlie已經有男朋友或者有啲兵仔陪佢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2156e8cc79bf53de7c72c42cdbb5759ebcbb07","tid":804820,"uid":24665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:30:05.000Z","msg":"Btw加油樓主"},{"pid":"6b12eca6a9eb71322860a4f44486125b7fa8c344","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:11:36.000Z","msg":"先向各位利申，些廢青真係現職於某大集團旗下咖啡店，如遲po故，還請各位體諒🙏🏻"},{"pid":"fea61c859af26484296c85afad2d87e584afdb71","tid":804820,"uid":206560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d421a52ad32a8b4b3561ee7ebc3cb36facf9d1a","tid":804820,"uid":98860,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:41:40.000Z","msg":"寫到真人真事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:24:42.000Z","msg":"唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真人真事會好向左走向右走sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c5693eabcc88b58137c09adc550fbc205248d0","tid":804820,"uid":153245,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:26:56.000Z","msg":"睇咗少少 排版令我無興趣睇落去"},{"pid":"c487e9c17f281cd73554bfde05861153f543f44a","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c5693eabcc88b58137c09adc550fbc205248d0","tid":804820,"uid":153245,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:26:56.000Z","msg":"睇咗少少 排版令我無興趣睇落去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:35:48.000Z","msg":"明白，些廢青會po得鬆動啲，令大家既眼球舒服啲，謝指教🙏🏻"},{"pid":"d052801e32b44c020430f48e2125742b3528fc35","tid":804820,"uid":20324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"Lm 推post"},{"pid":"5004c8f758437dc09b5240ced4fed815f029aa8b","tid":804820,"uid":52221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:03:58.000Z","msg":"正評留名"},{"pid":"137cb048bfaf66a260074483f888138ffca73feb","tid":804820,"uid":123497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"爽啦"},{"pid":"6ba4b13a0e994fb502ff04d58ef300157b9f7772","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"然而正當我想鼓起勇氣同charlie表白既時候<br />\n<br />\ncharlie已經同左經理講辭職<br />\n<br />\n所有通訊軟體都搵唔到charlie<br />\n<br />\n就彷彿係我既世界入面消失左一樣<br />\n<br />\n無論我點樣努力去搵都搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n直到有日聽到其中一個伙伴講<br />\n<br />\n話charlie去左外國發展<br />\n<br />\n因為有位外國人非常賞識charlie既手工作品<br />\n<br />\n而charlie遲遲都唔應承<br />\n<br />\n係最近先突然話要去外國<br />\n<br />\n於是我都懷住祝福charlie既心情去放棄搵佢<br />\n<br />\n如果...如果當初我唔係咁懦弱<br />\n<br />\n如果當初唔係咁自卑<br />\n<br />\n就唔會搞成依家咁..."},{"pid":"8d23af0aec880d0b2e65235169ee66dc1c85ea5f","tid":804820,"uid":27939,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"排左衰過未排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你再學下先出文啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb92f0d56faf0a63fd2bfac4fa172b865969520d","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"男主既居住理景<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/135648_a5b2e96b2b1c8e543b146f37e0b345c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F135648_a5b2e96b2b1c8e543b146f37e0b345c6.png&h=af7a41aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8be04898607068aff3107567340fc2ca5654c4c1","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb92f0d56faf0a63fd2bfac4fa172b865969520d","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"男主既居住理景<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/135648_a5b2e96b2b1c8e543b146f37e0b345c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F135648_a5b2e96b2b1c8e543b146f37e0b345c6.png&h=af7a41aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"環境"},{"pid":"1f2a5ab1e0bff49f7fc233abab2a91ff78a1fb58","tid":804820,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:08:26.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"294077abfb8c8e976da62bc30c0f673a525680e1","tid":804820,"uid":206560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fb92f0d56faf0a63fd2bfac4fa172b865969520d","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"男主既居住理景<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/135648_a5b2e96b2b1c8e543b146f37e0b345c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F135648_a5b2e96b2b1c8e543b146f37e0b345c6.png&h=af7a41aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31ca38b50d7c5bad38641ddc0ce6d5e1dbffc00","tid":804820,"uid":13383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:07:54.000Z","msg":"提議將唔同人嘅對話分返開，間中分下段，咁會好睇啲。"},{"pid":"7b3da14cba7cc6df4cab881a8da5a625ab9f3365","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:38:32.000Z","msg":"被擱置既情感要獨自一個面對，除左滿滿既悔恨同心酸，都要繼續迎接人生，且行且珍惜。<br />\n<br />\n       唔知最近係咪我既錯覺，感覺上via好似成日都會係我身邊出現，時不時會過嚟敲我床門問下我一啲瑣碎事，又或者直頭坐係我舖頭度一日，好似等我收工咁，又會成日約我落街食野，話時話，平日知性成熟既via面對住美食當前，就會好似個小朋友咁，食到成嘴都係污污糟糟咁，成日都要我幫佢抹，抹完之後又會比個傻大姐既笑容我，不過我都樂在其中既，但有時會諗，如果當初我同charlie一齊左，會唔會都好似依家咁呢？<br />\n<br />\n但我都想多謝via同阿恆佢地一齊陪我渡過左呢個傷痛。<br />\n<br />\n        今日返到公司，我既主任麗麗問我：「你同charlie係咪有啲小脾氣咋？點解無啦啦話走就走既？」<br />\n<br />\n我慚愧苦笑道：「都怪自己呆頭呆腦，明知對方既心意，都無鼓起勇氣接受，無架喇，一去不復返架喇。」<br />\n<br />\n麗麗安慰：「咁...都唔洗灰心啦，仲有我地咁多伙伴撐住你，阿jo加油啊！」<br />\n<br />\n呢個舖頭既伙伴都真係唔話得，當初我一入職咩都唔識咩都做錯，但佢地都好包容我體諒我，有咩私人問題都會比意見我，我真心覺得能夠入到呢間舖頭同大家共事真係我既福氣。"},{"pid":"92d5d6eaf05ef84a43f8ab82dd1c6c7a012a2779","tid":804820,"uid":13383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T12:04:26.000Z","msg":"咁樣易睇咗，已正評。"},{"pid":"ebdac0815d5040025332502278d358761fb78a01","tid":804820,"uid":93199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T12:10:53.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"dca154007c4f581c932a353c3d3123be248df401","tid":804820,"uid":206560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"文呀我要文呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9c2387a2864e9b38b360e5cf3fb592d4943cc5","tid":804820,"uid":9457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"希拉里讓我下沉<br />\n喜歡你特朗普<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的我係黎推post"},{"pid":"f6a281be2eac2a9c34216f3606c7065dd5519867","tid":804820,"uid":206896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f73a026884994f50b557fe3e2821a07b08c73327","tid":804820,"uid":124891,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:54:43.000Z","msg":"譚詠麟既愛情陷阱？"},{"pid":"6cfff9c127cfcfd73a4ec2e7f1a9e2d6d594f8d1","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T23:46:08.000Z","msg":"然而，今日via都坐係舖頭度，不過佢一接到個電話就面有難色咁走左，會唔會係有啲咩事呢？我都不禁擔心起上嚟，亦都想幫下via，可惜我仲未收工，就只能夠返到屋企先再問via，到我收工返到屋企既時候，搵哂成個單位都搵唔到via，大概via應該未返到屋企，所以我就係自己張床度等佢返嚟，不過因為我收工太攰既關係唔小心恰著左，到大概夜晚11點左右，我突然間聽到敲床位聲，於是我打開房門見到岩岩喊完既via，塊面仍然有未抹走既淚痕<br />\n<br />\n聲音沙啞卻強擠笑容道：「可唔可以入嚟比我坐陣陪下我啊？」<br />\n<br />\n我猛然起床讓出位置：「緊係可以啦，我知道妳應該出左啲事，同埋我特登早啲返嚟等妳架。」<br />\n<br />\nvia感動大哭抱緊我：「如果我遇到既男仔有你一半咁好就妳喇...」<br />\n<br />\n我微笑安慰：「傻瓜，無事架喇，仲記唔記得一開始我同妳講過咩架？妳有咩都可以問我拎架嘛，如果妳呢刻想我比個心妳既，咁妳拎去啦。」<br />\n<br />\nvia顯然被我既說話嚇到，但佢無縮開到，反而好安心咁依偎係我既懷裏，講左句：「jo，你真係一個好好既男仔，但你真係願意接受一個咁既我？」<br />\n<br />\n我：「只要妳一日都仲係妳，妳一日都仲係徐雅凝，我都會留係妳身邊照顧住妳。」<br />\n<br />\nvia驚訝：「咁樣值得咩？」<br />\n<br />\n我用堅定既眼神望住via：「無人話妳唔值得，只有妳覺得自己唔值得，仲有我覺得妳值得就得，過去既廿一年無人好好珍惜妳，但從今以後有我張家靖珍惜妳！」<br />\n<br />\nvia再無任何問題，只係不顧一切地撲向我，而我亦都準備好迎接via既一吻，之後我地就共渡左一個纏綿既夜晚。"},{"pid":"42b0cd24f97de4df22c44fad411123c368813573","tid":804820,"uid":97826,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T00:01:30.000Z","msg":"正皮支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bc82e0ea5703df29722dc4f4f96c04cd54eefb","tid":804820,"uid":145270,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T00:30:45.000Z","msg":"樓主 會唔會快左少少？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299e2477d2d83f3708c71979378acef1b4f68a94","tid":804820,"uid":71581,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:41:04.000Z","msg":"原來唔止我一個覺得跳得有d快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439ebabf84352e0b86821f99a6a845592b1bb422","tid":804820,"uid":51387,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n而我亦都準備好迎接via既一吻，之後我地就共渡左一個纏綿既夜晚。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來唔係甜故<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e0e0e142702b413f50da91a76b61f26e5137a1","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:17:34.000Z","msg":"一瞓醒就見到被我攬住左既via，瞓得好冧好安心，我都不禁錫左via額頭一啖，就係呢刻via醒左<br />\n<br />\n我擔心問：「係咪我整醒左妳啊？」<br />\n<br />\nvia用一個醉人既笑容望住我講：「傻瓜，唔係啊，我自己醒咋嘛，你起左身幾耐啊？有無比我壓到隻手痺左啊？」<br />\n<br />\n我撫摸著via個頭回答：「我都係岩岩起身咋，妳無壓到我隻手痺哂啊，不過我覺得成件事都好夢幻好唔真實啫。」<br />\n<br />\nvia甜笑道：「傻佬～你啊，要對我付責任啊，唔准好似我以前啲男朋友咁走左去架。」<br />\n<br />\n我自信滿滿地保證：「我已經係屬於妳架喇，想走都走唔甩。」via就嫣然一笑咁起身去左沖涼，而我亦都要去梳洗一下準備返工。<br />\n<br />\n        拖住via返到舖頭之後，麗麗既刻比左個意味深長既笑容我並係我換衫個陣諷刺道：「威啦你，咁快就有新女。」<br />\n<br />\n我迷惘道：「到呢刻我都仲覺得好夢幻好唔真實...」<br />\n<br />\n麗麗拍一拍我膊頭：「點都好啦，開心返就好，今晚收夜落力啲喇，可唔可以早走就睇你架喇，你都唔想你女朋友等你咁耐架！」<br />\n<br />\n我充滿幹勁：「無問題啦，就算無得早走都一定準時！」<br />\n<br />\n        今日係我企收銀，via走嚟收銀面前同我講：「今日我等埋你收工再一齊去食野啦～唔洗理我架，我想留意多啲你做野個樣，真係好吸引好靚仔～」<br />\n<br />\n 我尷尬道：「呢啲野留返係屋企先講啦，妳坐下先啦，我等等再沖杯野飲比妳啦。」<br />\n<br />\nvia甜笑：「好啦好啦～」<br />\n<br />\n於是乎接下來成日via都望實我做野，而我都沖左杯野飲比via並同佢講：「呢杯係caramel macchiato，意大利文既意思係甜蜜的烙印，寓意住我係妳心內面留下左一個甜蜜的烙印。」<br />\n<br />\nvia滿面通紅：「你個黑人憎啊，咁快就學人口花花，唔好以為自己靚仔就可以為所欲為啵！」<br />\n<br />\n原來蜜運中既via都係同小朋友一樣，不過始終係女仔，當然想比人氹比人錫啦，更何況呢個係via，比人傷透身心都依然相信愛情相信我，為左回答via既心意，我都要努力令via幸福。<br />\n<br />\n       同via返到屋企之後我心血來潮問via：「via，咁我地依家既關係係..？」<br />\n<br />\nvia漫不經心地回答：「唔知啊，你覺得呢？我自己就覺依家咁樣都唔錯啊，有啲關係唔需要太清楚，仲有啊，你真係放低左charlie喇咩？真係一刻都無當過我係佢？」<br />\n<br />\n我驚訝又失落地回答：「妳...妳講得都岩既...對唔住，我誤會左妳，打搞到妳真係唔好意思，無咩既話，我返上床先喇。」"},{"pid":"a474bf8055d63a8001373923ac6dc3aa2dee593e","tid":804820,"uid":123616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:42:53.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c3122a3ad0ae80a68fb195b7103794992f214453","tid":804820,"uid":189102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"皮己正~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be600aa452965eea657922f25c58911d716d25f0","tid":804820,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acba4a817c2cf9b417ec90a4bbcdece0d9f69397","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"其實各位會撐jo同via定charlie一齊多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935b6f5960972ce58830f9bc55bc13b2d0f465dc","tid":804820,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e009c244fbbbbcd5e5490ff9756a8ccb6f62de62","tid":804820,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105a3f1f0b1e6e1fec7e53b019b2902792b1493b","tid":804820,"uid":206560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"樓主 屎忽定出文 你揀"},{"pid":"96f81a05b2d6a439ae8f32fd33731f732c7856b8","tid":804820,"uid":202696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T18:06:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99f04cee4c01b2ba4db810daddaa6ef633746db6","tid":804820,"uid":146707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T22:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3e7b1d3fd58dbf4781c059f2fd6c00a0e9ae0a","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:07:05.000Z","msg":"原來只係我既一廂情願，我以為via會比我感動到，我以為我真係可以令via安心，但我既以後都只不過係我既以為，無力感向我一擁而襲，絕望正慢慢蠶食我既內心，突然覺得好攰好攰，然後我就因為傷心過度而進入夢鄉，彷彿想逃避一切，想一起身via會對住自己傻笑...<br />\n<br />\n      「咯咯咯...咯咯咯...」敲門聲<br />\n<br />\n我蒙蒙朧朧打開門，一把熟悉既聲音盡入我既腦海，係charlie...佢：「你可唔可以醒一醒陪下我啊？」<br />\n<br />\n我睡眼惺忪：「我...我...我好眼瞓...妳比我瞓多&amp;$@?!&yen;#%^*+....」<br />\n<br />\ncharlie大力搖晃道：「喂吔！你唔好瞓住先啦，起身陪陪我啦。」<br />\n<br />\n於是我一個反身甩開左charlie同時都令charlie失平衡仆落我度，就好似偶像劇橋段一樣，每個仆親都會伴隨住接吻，而我同charlie正正就係呢個狀況<br />\n<br />\n我回過神嚟打算扶起charlie並問：「妳有無事啊？」<br />\n<br />\n而charlie遲遲唔肯起身並撒嬌道：「可唔可以比我伏多陣啊？一路以嚟我所憧憬既就係我既生活有你，我想同你道歉，粒聲唔出咁一走了之，係外國既生活無你係我身邊，我真係覺得好寂寞...」<br />\n<br />\n我迷惘道：「係妳去左外國既日子我有試過不停咁去搵妳，有試過一沉百踩，亦都接受左妳已經唔係我身邊既事實，可唔可以比啲時間我諗下？」charlie堅定既眼神望住我：「好，我會比時間你。」"},{"pid":"56b43337f8bf51395e167d919ba0715b7bd11952","tid":804820,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:13:40.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3eba94077c8cfd274d27321fe5cdb104b796cc92","tid":804820,"uid":187076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:19:27.000Z","msg":"一拖二<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff22e01fd9a267ae3f64f3e58a743638ccbbb6c7","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:44:39.000Z","msg":"經過charlie返嚟呢一役之後，我同via既距離開始變返當初佢岩岩搬嚟住一樣，甚少既交雜，有時我刻意早放返屋企想撞到via，但通常via返到嚟既時間已經係我瞓緊瞓既時間，近呢兩日仲聽到格離床位既人話via每次返到嚟都成身煙酒味，對於via刻意疏遠自己既行動，我都不知如何是好，亦都覺得好唏噓，每次我想努力去維繫同via既關係，但via每次都避開我。"},{"pid":"eed45fdd33f965fe283739d5462384470f6f1952","tid":804820,"uid":16281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:55:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e556f20f0352163332eef60f1815de193feafc3e","tid":804820,"uid":206560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"推到世界盡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4a24d9febee7461fb67b9fafe46351b666474e","tid":804820,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3113d8e08e3aef29cc98dec55e5901960eee40","tid":804820,"uid":51387,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:33:02.000Z","msg":"好靈異, charlie之前基本上係一個同事關係, 但又識得走上去主角床位搵佢. <br />\n<br />\n其實via是咪charlie假扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07255e427792113120a45217424f315016deb678","tid":804820,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"快"},{"pid":"15489a41c5a6b825960136475add4a39b24a58a8","tid":804820,"uid":199101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e3f26cae247426686ddb7b5ea08997fef73b5e0","tid":804820,"uid":78557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:13:11.000Z","msg":"推一推先"},{"pid":"3fdc5638b19e3bd90c20932e7eee1600a8ce5caa","tid":804820,"uid":30777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"pu推sh"},{"pid":"3316e81ab5fb917db8d989a4fde6eb83d104379f","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:53:10.000Z","msg":"係呢段期間，charlie已經同左經理講返返嚟做，如charlie仲係我身邊既時候一樣，一齊去食飯，一齊收工走，但係，我已經搵唔返當初既感覺，反而個腦一直諗住via，諗返起via同我既一點一滴，諗返起via既溫柔同善解人意，諗返起via既一切一切，但係charlie今次返嚟都係因為我而放棄左加拿大個邊既發展，所以我好自責，當初無好好珍惜charlie，依家人地直頭放棄所有野嚟比多次機會我，今次我係咪應該要珍惜？"},{"pid":"73890929b25c6e58c9829594d70dbb76f9bddf07","tid":804820,"uid":46931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:48:20.000Z","msg":"請加甜。"},{"pid":"7296500da108f49d7db082fb07aabf4e737c9ebd","tid":804820,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f73a026884994f50b557fe3e2821a07b08c73327","tid":804820,"uid":124891,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:54:43.000Z","msg":"譚詠麟既愛情陷阱？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T11:13:28.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"da53771fda576a50694df494878f58ceef5e19c1","tid":804820,"uid":206560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229481283030736c8cb7d88e666bb7ec9b0a8973","tid":804820,"uid":146707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T22:07:14.000Z","msg":"Via慘豬"},{"pid":"e6bbbc0a1619facf9781a5367231d61f424e73d6","tid":804820,"uid":13395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T23:18:51.000Z","msg":"Via <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0715e90b791a075ae7889ac0eb389434b34dd11","tid":804820,"uid":71496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T23:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f55e472e51a79281815785853c312708c31a240","tid":804820,"uid":62245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cit