ssets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68debb9cdfbd9ff33cd6c824cbe101f3f441607d","tid":804820,"uid":138775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0b7feb92bc0044879f2f8be02f0f9fdd3ecc1fd","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8a720dc4bd5df973c93f7fc8c419cee3a4055a7","tid":804820,"uid":33147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89f6c9c3c357b3f1cc056c9ea6eb15d264b32718","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"例如呢？<br />\n我盡量滿足你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:45:14.000Z","msg":"例如Charlie 點解返嚟 點解知樓主住邊等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"之後會以via同charlie視覺寫下架喇<br />\n等下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"快啲update 頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18bbfe47cd63b498dc50a04346362f241ba2161","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:50:55.000Z","msg":"然而，如平常既一晚，但我突然間聽到個廳好多吵鬧聲，我出左去望，見到via飲到爛醉係咁亂講野，其他人都手足無措<br />\n<br />\n因為via一直係度講：「你班咸濕佬唔好掂我啊！可以掂我既男人就只有一個！就只有張家靖一個可以掂我！」<br />\n<br />\n係房門口聽到一切既我已經唔識得比反應，而且via已經同我對上左視線，除即行過嚟攬住我講：「你個衰人！你遲鈍啊！咁都察覺唔到！如果唔係個個乜鬼野charlie返左嚟啊！我先無咁輕易放你走啊！」<br />\n<br />\n聽到呢度，我覺得好窩心，就算只係via既醉言醉語又好，未必係真既都好，至少比我知道我係via個心入面留下左一個位置，然後就要處理埋via嘔到周圍係既地方，抱返via上床，幫佢換衫再望住via瞓覺，via瞓緊覺個樣真係好迷人，但我都比忙碌左一日既倦意侵襲，就返左上床瞓。<br />\n<br />\n        翌日，起梳洗既時候，見到via岩岩係廁所出嚟，靦腆地問：「尋晚係你一直照顧我？」<br />\n<br />\n我：「係啊，不過妳飲到斷哂片都應該唔記得架喇」<br />\n<br />\nvia羞愧：「咁我有無亂咁講野啊？」<br />\n<br />\n我取笑道：「都無既...不過就係咁大嗌我個名咁囉...」<br />\n<br />\nvia黯住塊面：「真係失禮，不過點都好，多謝你照顧左我一晚。」<br />\n<br />\n我：「都係個句啦，有咩問題就搵我啦。」<br />\n<br />\nvia微笑：「好，多謝你。」<br />\n<br />\n我拍一拍via膊頭：「客咩氣啊，我等等要返工喇，收工再傾啦。」via點一點頭，我就入左廁所梳洗。"},{"pid":"0cf29f414d3cc6c55eba32752c8dce5b1454736a","tid":804820,"uid":204299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出阿出阿<br />\n<br />\nbtw 辛苦樓主"},{"pid":"3ebf18da6780c9f9ef899a796cf3837c5f08e5aa","tid":804820,"uid":189102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:38:05.000Z","msg":"終於長啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e90cc4b9cad8cdab442ed453f26e9d9ae1d83b","tid":804820,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd11e81e07c1fdb4550ef6b887130c7a245472f2","tid":804820,"uid":17847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2f0d5efcc2b7d86ae217221083e8f61b0a9d2b","tid":804820,"uid":147617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"今日冇文？"},{"pid":"afbad1b937893b19d171101215778eed3e7d3eb0","tid":804820,"uid":206328,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:23:59.000Z","msg":"返到舖頭，經理阿景就叫左我入經理室<br />\n<br />\n阿景話：「jo，我知你最近比啲私人問題困擾住，可能係工作上面會有啲落差，不過我明既，有咩需要同我講，我幫到你就幫啦。」<br />\n<br />\n我：「多謝體諒，我會繼續盡力做好。」阿景：「好，咁你出返去做野先啦。」<br />\n<br />\n        一出到去，charlie就問：「阿景啱啱同你講左啲咩啊？係咪鬧你啊？」<br />\n<br />\n我：「無咩野啊，普通傾下閒計啫。」<br />\n<br />\ncharlie用一個質疑既眼神望住我並道：「係咪真架？」<br />\n<br />\n我無奈：「係啊，真係無比人鬧啊，放心啦。」<br />\n<br />\n於是charlie就恢復笑容：「咁好啦，係呢，晏晝食咩好啊我地？」<br />\n<br />\n我諗左一陣之後，就話：「不如食吉仔？我好似好耐無食過飯。」<br />\n<br />\ncharlie：「好啊，就食吉仔啦～」<br />\n<br />\n        見到仍然仲咁天真咁信任我既charlie，內心不禁泛起一種內疚，好想補償返比佢，但係我真係諗唔到方法點樣去補償，不過我已經一心向住via，唔想再做啲動作去令charlie誤會，我只係想對via好照顧via，想同charlie講清楚，過去左就過去左，已經返唔到轉頭，希望charlie以後可以搵到一個好男仔去錫佢，可惜我無呢個勇氣同charlie講清楚，只能夠慢慢疏遠charlie。<br />\n<br />\n         食完飯之後，返舖頭見到via坐左係度飲caramel macchiato，但係當via見到charlie之後就面色一沉，杯咖啡都未飲完就走左，可惜既係我仲返緊工，如果唔係我一定追出去陪via，不過charlie又係我身邊，唯有等收工返到屋企先再搵via啦。"},{"pid":"aa6097fe958344ef1316e299345fd4b621e77b7f","tid":804820,"uid":206560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96d8ff5510d431a90bbe769c2d82c72b248310f","tid":804820,"uid":22095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:27:32.000Z","msg":"其實呢個charlie返嚟香港 係樓主諗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本就冇返過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52813cb56705c13d214e8bbe645103ff74f6ab74","tid":804820,"uid":178728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcbd5a09a708f5650f5d785aa94f7d65816b6f00","tid":804820,"uid":146707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T22:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ac559b45f7a56f1ddba393bcd62fec07176f4c","tid":804820,"uid":206560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  返工好悶呀 有文未"}]}